New Records: Cole Ragans matched a franchise record with eight consecutive strikeouts through the third inning.
Key Match Events: Yusei Kikuchi struck out 12 over seven strong innings.
Yanier Diaz hit a two-run single.
Jeremy Pena hit a two-run triple.
Bobby Witt Jr. hit his 29th home run with two outs in the eighth inning.
Post-Match Reflections: Astros manager Joe Espada praised Kikuchi's performance, stating he had all his pitches working and the defense was really good behind him.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Royals have dropped four consecutive games, while the Astros have won four in a row.
